title: Knicks fire Thibodeau after best run in 25 years
description: The Knicks are firing head coach Tom Thibodeau just a week after he led the team to its first Eastern Conference finals in 25 years.

title: More men allege sexual misconduct by ex-IU doc
description: At least 15 former Indiana men's basketball players are alleging improper sexual conduct by a former team physician and saying Indiana officials, including the late coach Bobby Knight, were aware of the behavior.
